00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:36,465
There's one particular surfer
who's turned silly...

245
00:19:36,549 --> 00:19:39,301
into something downright heroic.

246
00:19:39,385 --> 00:19:42,804
I was working at
this refried chicken place...

247
00:19:42,888 --> 00:19:46,432
