249
00:19:50,853 --> 00:19:54,481
I would've happily left
after five minutes.

250
00:19:54,564 --> 00:19:56,523
To have lasted eight hours there...

251
00:19:56,608 --> 00:19:59,068
was the longest eight hours
I've ever experienced.

252
00:20:01,278 --> 00:20:04,072
Dale Webster does not like
wasting time.

253
00:20:04,197 --> 00:20:06,073
With mind-boggling dedication...

254
00:20:06,199 --> 00:20:10,077
he has committed to a goal so simple
it would seem impossible.

255
00:20:10,202 --> 00:20:14,705
Today was 9, 1 82 consecutive days...

256
00:20:14,831 --> 00:20:16,874
a little over 25 years.

257
00:20:18,042 --> 00:20:19,960
I'm trying to surf...

258
00:20:20,044 --> 00:20:22,212
to the year 2004...

259
00:20:22,338 --> 00:20:27,467
and by then I'll be
up to 1 0,407 consecutive days.

260
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:31,678
If I can reach that goal, you can tell
