261
00:20:31,804 --> 00:20:35,432
Every day,
rain or shine or tonsillitis...

262
00:20:35,557 --> 00:20:38,517
Dale's out there,
mano a mano with the calendar.

263
00:20:38,601 --> 00:20:41,686
In February 1 976...

264
00:20:41,812 --> 00:20:43,730
there were five Sundays in a row...

265
00:20:43,814 --> 00:20:47,233
