00:20:56,825 --> 00:20:59,702
He's kept everything on his pursuit.

269
00:20:59,786 --> 00:21:03,789
It started out as a streak,
it went into a quest...

270
00:21:03,914 --> 00:21:05,456
and now it's some sort of a mission.

271
00:21:06,291 --> 00:21:08,376
I don't really know
what the mission is...

272
00:21:08,460 --> 00:21:10,378
but the only worthwhile thing in life...

273
00:21:10,461 --> 00:21:13,296
is to ride it to the end...

274
00:21:13,422 --> 00:21:15,757
try to find out
the meaning of it all.

