00:45:50,872 --> 00:45:53,207
which is great,
'cause Taj is quite creative.

667
00:45:53,332 --> 00:45:56,960
Creativity is one of the most
magical things about surfing...

668
00:45:57,043 --> 00:45:59,336
and also one of
the most difficult to judge.

669
00:46:09,679 --> 00:46:13,974
It's gonna take a long time
for us to really catch up to speed...

670
00:46:14,058 --> 00:46:15,976
with Taj's level.

671
00:46:16,059 --> 00:46:18,602
Gonna take a while for the judges
