00:46:23,357 --> 00:46:25,817
as far as how many maneuvers
he packs in a wave...

674
00:46:25,901 --> 00:46:29,112
how innovative he is
when he launches air.

675
00:46:34,992 --> 00:46:37,619
Taj, by any measure,
is a great success.

676
00:46:37,703 --> 00:46:41,581
At 23 he's already been inducted
